room_title: Escape room "Vintage Circus" by Granite State Escape in Manchester
room_description: The Circus is in town! Popcorn is popping, tigers are roaring, performers are dazzling folks of all ages! But behind the big-top, hides a dark secret… patrons are disappearing. As you search for an answer, you notice a dimly lit sign that reads “Dr. Oswaldo’s Oddities - Shows Every Hour.” Most scurry past, but you can’t control your curiosity and wander inside.
